<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Subscription Cancellation Confirmation</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #f44336;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 5px 5px 0 0;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 0 0 5px 5px;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #2196F3;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>Subscription Cancellation Confirmation</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
        <p>Dear {{name}},</p>
        
        <p>We're sorry to see you go. Your subscription has been cancelled as requested.</p>
        
        <h2>Cancellation Details:</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Plan: {{planName}}</li>
            <li>Access until: {{endDate}}</li>
            {{#if reason}}
            <li>Reason: {{reason}}</li>
            {{/if}}
        </ul>

        <p>Your subscription will remain active until {{endDate}}. After this date, you will lose access to premium features.</p>

        <p>If you change your mind, you can reactivate your subscription at any time before {{endDate}}.</p>

        <a href="{{baseUrl}}/subscription/reactivate" class="button">Reactivate Subscription</a>

        <p>We value your feedback. If you have any suggestions on how we could improve our service, please let us know.</p>
        
        <p>Best regards,<br>The WhatsApp Tool Team</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
        <p>This is an automated message, please do not reply directly to this email.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 